### ===== PROPOSAL ENDPOINTS =====


### Get All Proposals
GET http://localhost:3001/api/proposals


### Get Proposal by ID (id=2)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/proposals/2

### Create Proposal (userId=2, member sameer)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/proposals
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 2,
    "description": "Upgrade office equipment and computers",
    "cost": 5000
}

### Create Another Proposal (userId=3, member rafay)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/proposals
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 3,
    "description": "Team building and training program",
    "cost": 3000
}

### Update Proposal (id=1)
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/proposals/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "Upgrade office equipment with latest technology and software",
    "cost": 6000
}

### Delete Proposal (id=1)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/proposals/2